<P>AN ACT OF COMMON COUNCIL For the better Regulation of WEIGHING OF GOODS and MERCHANDIZES AT THE KING'S BEAMS.</P>
<P><FIGURE>
<FIGDESC>arms of London</FIGDESC>
</FIGURE></P>
<P>Printed by <HI>Samuel <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="MURP" EXTENT="1 chunk">cr<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="MURP" EXTENT="1 letter">ft,</HI> Printer to the Honourable City of <HI>LONDON,</HI> 1698.</P>
